95617 is one of the three zip codes in Davis. It is used only for Shipping Services post office boxes. The other two are used for streets physical locations in Davis and are 95616 (for roughly the West Davis west and North Davis northern parts of Davis) and 95618 (for the East Davis eastern and South Davis southern parts).

It is officially centered at Latitude 38.5494, Longitude 121.7253 and an elevation of 41 feet.
